                                       Gapps for khadas

About how to add Gapps support on khadas VIMs and Edge SDK source code, You can follow the steps below

一、VIMs board
1. Modify the file 'PROJECT/device/khadas/kvim.mk' or 'PROJECT/device/khadas/kvim2.mk'
<1> Change the property 'BUILD_WITH_GAPPS_CONFIG' from false to true

2. Download the google repertory into the path 'PROJECT/vendor/amlogic/'
<1> cd PROJECT/vendor/amlogic/
<2> git clone https://github.com/terry2droid/google google -b Nougat

3. Build yourself ROM again

二、Edge board
1. Modify the file 'PROJECT/device/rockchip/rk3399/rk3399_all.mk'
<1> Change the property 'BUILD_WITH_GAPPS_CONFIG' from false to true

2. Download the google repertory into the path 'PROJECT/vendor/rockchip/'
<1> cd PROJECT/vendor/rockchip/
<2> git clone https://github.com/terry2droid/google google -b Nougat

3. Build yourself ROM again
 
